  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Description of Enspell Game</h2><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396900/extras/e62d21234673aef9eed3b5271d5e1635.poster.avif?t=1707120053\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396900/extras/e62d21234673aef9eed3b5271d5e1635.webm?t=1707120053\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396900/extras/e62d21234673aef9eed3b5271d5e1635.mp4?t=1707120053\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>“Enspell” is deck building-RogueLike game based on a medieval fantasy where you unravel secrets and explore to seek treasures. <br>While you fight against monsters in dangerous dungeons, you can collect relics and make your own deck.<br>Establish strategies with new decks every time and reach the end of the Dungeon, which is the final goal, and discover the secret in the castle!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396900/extras/7e44bd9f78dbaa1ce33be48c072b585f.poster.avif?t=1707120053\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396900/extras/7e44bd9f78dbaa1ce33be48c072b585f.webm?t=1707120053\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396900/extras/7e44bd9f78dbaa1ce33be48c072b585f.mp4?t=1707120053\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Battle with Card Replacement</strong><br>Replace cards during battles to pick up cards properly for situations and make the cards stronger through replacing them.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396900/extras/ed02fefe67c9d8aff6aa7f018d57fab9.avif?t=1707120053\" width=600 height=300 /></span><br><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Monster Deck</strong><br>Monsters also do battles by picking up cards from the deck in the same way as players.<br>So you should think about which card you will use in this turn according to the cards picked by the monster!<br><br><br></li><li><strong>The Changing map</strong><br>The structure of the map changes for every new play.<br>Make the best path for you and grow up through strategic battles.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396900/extras/59f059c9a03eba7c79872316371a3bbb.avif?t=1707120053\" width=600 height=300 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game goals</h2>It is necessary to make wise choices at the crossroads of various choices to make the main character go into the deepest place of the dungeon.<br>Finally, you should win the final battle against the enemy in the deepest place of the dungeon so that the main character can achieve the true goal!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396900/extras/c1ec664920eedff9a29508c0b8c81cb1.poster.avif?t=1707120053\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396900/extras/c1ec664920eedff9a29508c0b8c81cb1.webm?t=1707120053\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396900/extras/c1ec664920eedff9a29508c0b8c81cb1.mp4?t=1707120053\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Description of Enspell Game</h2><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396900/extras/e62d21234673aef9eed3b5271d5e1635.poster.avif?t=1707120053\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396900/extras/e62d21234673aef9eed3b5271d5e1635.webm?t=1707120053\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396900/extras/e62d21234673aef9eed3b5271d5e1635.mp4?t=1707120053\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>“Enspell” is deck building-RogueLike game based on a medieval fantasy where you unravel secrets and explore to seek treasures. <br>While you fight against monsters in dangerous dungeons, you can collect relics and make your own deck.<br>Establish strategies with new decks every time and reach the end of the Dungeon, which is the final goal, and discover the secret in the castle!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396900/extras/7e44bd9f78dbaa1ce33be48c072b585f.poster.avif?t=1707120053\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396900/extras/7e44bd9f78dbaa1ce33be48c072b585f.webm?t=1707120053\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396900/extras/7e44bd9f78dbaa1ce33be48c072b585f.mp4?t=1707120053\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Battle with Card Replacement</strong><br>Replace cards during battles to pick up cards properly for situations and make the cards stronger through replacing them.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396900/extras/ed02fefe67c9d8aff6aa7f018d57fab9.avif?t=1707120053\" width=600 height=300 /></span><br><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Monster Deck</strong><br>Monsters also do battles by picking up cards from the deck in the same way as players.<br>So you should think about which card you will use in this turn according to the cards picked by the monster!<br><br><br></li><li><strong>The Changing map</strong><br>The structure of the map changes for every new play.<br>Make the best path for you and grow up through strategic battles.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396900/extras/59f059c9a03eba7c79872316371a3bbb.avif?t=1707120053\" width=600 height=300 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game goals</h2>It is necessary to make wise choices at the crossroads of various choices to make the main character go into the deepest place of the dungeon.<br>Finally, you should win the final battle against the enemy in the deepest place of the dungeon so that the main character can achieve the true goal!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396900/extras/c1ec664920eedff9a29508c0b8c81cb1.poster.avif?t=1707120053\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396900/extras/c1ec664920eedff9a29508c0b8c81cb1.webm?t=1707120053\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396900/extras/c1ec664920eedff9a29508c0b8c81cb1.mp4?t=1707120053\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
